\id 2PE - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014)
\h 2 Pit
\toc3 2 Pit
\toc1 Pitakono Naba 2 Leta Ebete Hibimaęž‰ Midipaęž‰tamo Ododiyaęž‰
\toc2 2 Pita
\mt1 PITAKONO NABA 2 LETA
\mt2 EBETE HIBIMAęž‰ MIDIPAęž‰TAMO ODODIYAęž‰
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Na baęž‰ Saimono Pitatela, Yaęž‰su Kelisokono okodawala, iyo, ebete ebeno sose tupuimimaęž‰ hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hopamo doelamiyaęž‰, baęž‰bi okopi ipuwalo na baęž‰ etala.
\p Baęž‰ hibila, Yaęž‰su Kelisoko baęž‰ aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawala, ebe baęž‰ Godotela. Baęž‰gala ebete ebeno tuputupu ododili gabodo puyaęž‰tamo hibimaęž‰ midi komo dikalamiyaęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰ baęž‰bi tawakalubilata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ nale baęž‰moe leta laęž‰tamo poememo, mabu laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi komo baęž‰gala aeno hibimaęž‰ midi komo baęž‰ kapiyanomola.
\p 
\v 2 Wadiyala laęž‰ Godokono komo baęž‰gala aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰sukunu komo ba iyaęž‰tawaha, ibino malemale komo baęž‰gala ibino hete komote laęž‰godolo konomamo naęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰.
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midi Ipuwalo Apepeho Komo
\p 
\v 3 Baęž‰ hibila, dopamo tetelo Yaęž‰suti a aęž‰kaęž‰miyaęž‰ ale ebeno helonomo alago baęž‰gala ebeno tuputupu ododili komago kemedehonamaęž‰. Ebegodolo Godokono helote bitana baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete atamo hiliyonomo hidohido komo ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰, ale ebeno komo ba iyaęž‰tawaha Godokono ubi komamo hibilo kopapamilaęž‰hanamaęž‰.
\v 4 Iyo, ebete dopamo a kowalubimaęž‰ kebe tabo hibilo daęž‰goiyaęž‰, baęž‰be taboeno hibi komote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na uluhukuyaęž‰, ebete atamo kokonomo komo baęž‰gala hidohidonomo komo dito ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰, mabu ebe ubila ale hopo tawakalubino kateneno kuba ododili ipuwane ikuliti aeno emede ipuwalo ale Godokomo kemedehonamaęž‰.
\p 
\v 5 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ laęž‰le laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo apepeho wakolado kalehawaminamaęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno ukui konomamo nihatenalaęž‰. Iyo, laęž‰ baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na Godoko hibimaęž‰ ba midina, ebeno tuputupu emede komo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰bene laęž‰ tuputupulu ba emedehona, Godokono hibi iyaęž‰tawa komo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰.
\v 6 Baęž‰bene laęž‰ Godokono komo hibilo ba iyaęž‰tawahana, Godokono helo lawemaęž‰ tepo kodakoda komo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰bene laęž‰ tepo kodakodalo ba laęž‰motaęž‰hana, koko temeteme ipuwalo helohaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰haheno kalakala naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰bene laęž‰ temeteme ipuwalo helohaęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰haheno ba laęž‰motaęž‰hana, Godotamo hibilo papamiwata komo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰.
\v 7 Baęž‰bene Godotamo hibilo ba papamilaęž‰hana, laęž‰ komo hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo malemale hawakalimi komo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰bene laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo malemale ba hawakalimina, wadiyala Godokono malemale emalagidolo komote hopo habanapi hiliyonomatamo laęž‰ ipuwalo konomomaęž‰ nedaęž‰mene.
\p 
\v 8 Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰moi apepeho wakoloeno komo hiliyonomate laęž‰godolo konomamo daęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo laęž‰ aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono hibi komo ba iyaęž‰tawaha ebeno hidohido gao noloho oko bowatihonamata.
\v 9 Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, kebe hibimaęž‰ midi lumagigodolo baęž‰bi komokomate polaęž‰naheno, ebe baęž‰ baidi tamihodawala, iyo, ebeno emede komote baęž‰moe komo behawakalimina, Yaęž‰suti ebe ebeno kuba ododili ipuwane uluhukutiti ebeno tepo ipuwa dukulamiyaęž‰, ebete baęž‰be hido komo yaęž‰lo adodui.
\v 10 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno ekakaęž‰laęž‰, Godote laęž‰ dopamo daęž‰kaęž‰lamiholiyaęž‰ baęž‰be komo hibilo kohawakalimimaęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo helohelonomomaęž‰ nedaęž‰huyaęž‰laęž‰, mabu hibila, laęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na dewagelema laęž‰ nato ukamidahalete aęž‰kagudaęž‰mata.
\v 11 Iyo, baęž‰moe baęž‰be gabodo Godote laęž‰tamo gigiho kaęž‰hiyaęž‰midalamemaęž‰naęž‰ta, laęž‰le aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawoeno kalakala emede habamo konaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰hamaęž‰, baęž‰be Kodawa baęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisotela baęž‰gala ebeno Ko Gawadubumaęž‰ edaęž‰ komote emedena emedena tetelo bitanamene.
\s1 Pitate Ebeno Hoe Komo Tatalimaęž‰ Daęž‰goiyaęž‰
\p 
\v 12 Baęž‰ hibila, laęž‰ baęž‰moi komokomo yaęž‰lo iyaęž‰tawahuyaęž‰mata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godote laęž‰tamo dikalamiyaęž‰la laęž‰ baęž‰be hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo helomaęž‰ edaęž‰hanamata. Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, naeno kalakala bitana komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tetelo baęž‰moi atu komo laęž‰ gala kakakiyalamenakomaęž‰,
\v 13 baęž‰bemaęž‰ na hoeheno dopamo laęž‰ baęž‰moi komo gala daęž‰kakiyalamema, baęž‰be komo baęž‰ hido komola.
\v 14 Iyo, na iyaęž‰tawala tete tatalila na baęž‰ kohoemaęž‰nemo, mabu aeno Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisote baęž‰moe komo na yaęž‰lo iyaęž‰tunami.
\v 15 Baęž‰moe baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ baęž‰moe leta ipuwalo nale baęž‰moi komokomo laęž‰ gala baęž‰bemaęž‰ kakiyalamemata, naeno hoe gala hapuni laęž‰le baęž‰moi komo hidamo kemalagidolenamaęž‰.
\s1 Godokono Ukui Hawakalimipaęž‰te Yaęž‰suku Mabumaęž‰ Bukamo Hibi Tabo Komokomo Daęž‰miyaęž‰tiyaęž‰
\p 
\v 16 Numaęž‰laęž‰, a Kodawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono oelamepaęž‰te ebeno helo komo baęž‰gala hawakala komo laęž‰tamo daęž‰pehawakalimiyaęž‰maęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ale laęž‰ haęž‰da kamiholamiyaęž‰haęž‰. Baęž‰gala komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tawakalubino iniwalaęž‰te ibi haęž‰kiya ibino kapiyuimi mabumaęž‰ eyoni gugudaęž‰tamo kebako uwi kaęž‰kiyahanakui, ale baęž‰bako tawakalubino uwi komokomo laęž‰ kakiyahalamiyaęž‰haęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, ale Yaęž‰sukunu Ko Gawadubu helo aeno baidaęž‰mo dumiyaęž‰maęž‰, baęž‰be komo laęž‰ aęž‰kiyalamiyaęž‰ta,
\v 17 mabu Nabiwi Godote Yaęž‰suku ba milimiho ebe dawagaminutiyaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo komo a ebeno oelamepaęž‰te baęž‰bolo naęž‰polaęž‰nuyaęž‰maęž‰. Baęž‰bene ale aeno galamo Ko Alonomodawoeno tabo madodo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na uliyaęž‰maęž‰, â€śBaęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno kapiya Gudunomola. Na ebetamo naęž‰kalakalutamo!â€ť
\v 18 Iyo, a Yaęž‰sukubaęž‰ talona hununomo hakalo daęž‰polaęž‰nuyaęž‰maęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo Godokono tabo madodote ebeno Hunu Habane atamo baęž‰ba kaęž‰na puluhukuyaęž‰.
\p 
\v 19 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godokono ukui hawakalimipaęž‰te Yaęž‰suku mabumaęž‰ Bukamo yaęž‰lo tetelo daęž‰miyaęž‰tiyaęž‰, ale baęž‰bi komokomo hibimaęž‰ naęž‰midilinamaęž‰. Numaęž‰laęž‰, ibino tabo komokomo baęž‰ alo dehaęž‰potote konomo du ipuwalo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰laęž‰minana baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala, baęž‰bene tete tatalila Huli Olokiti haęž‰kiya kuluhukumaęž‰ne, iyo, baęž‰ba tetelo hido hegelate ba powaloho duino hilibubuti dito kowibomaęž‰ne. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, baęž‰be alote laęž‰eno tepo ipuwalo hidamo kaęž‰laęž‰minalemaęž‰, wadiyala laęž‰ Godokono okopaęž‰te dopamo daęž‰hawakalimiyaęž‰ baęž‰be tabo hibimaęž‰ miditi hidonomamo naęž‰lawiyaęž‰laęž‰.
\v 20 Baęž‰gala baęž‰moe ko komo hidamo niyaęž‰tawahalaęž‰. Godokono ukui hawakalimipaęž‰te ebeno Bukamo dopamo kebe tabo komokomo kaęž‰miyaęž‰tiyaęž‰, lumagiti haęž‰kiya ebeno mulu ukuiaęž‰mo baęž‰bi taboeno ipuwa uwate modobohaęž‰,
\v 21 mabu Godokono ukui hawakalimipaęž‰te ibi haęž‰kiya ibino ubilo ibino ukui tabo Bukamo kamiyaęž‰tenakuihaęž‰. Ao, Godokono Gobogobote ibi keba kaęž‰na kiyaęž‰tulamenakui, ibaęž‰te ebeno tabonomo Bukamo miyaęž‰telo baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na olamagiminakuyaęž‰.
\c 2
\s1 Godokono Mahilamo Haęž‰da Tabo Olamagimipaęž‰te Ikuli Komo
\p 
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰eno iniwalino tetelo Godokono hibi tabo olamagimipaęž‰te oko ba owatina, atu tetelo Godokono mahilamo haęž‰da tabo olamagimipaęž‰te aęž‰mahilaęž‰halenakuyaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰ma tetelo komo baęž‰bakobako dubate laęž‰ ipuwalo gala kakikulimaęž‰naęž‰. Baęž‰baęž‰te laęž‰eno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo kokubahilamemaęž‰ ibino haęž‰da tabo komokomo kolamagimimaęž‰naęž‰, baęž‰bene kebe dawate ibino kuba ododili komoeno helo ipuwane ibi ebeno hawaęž‰mo malemalelo duluhukulateliyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te ebe ubihaęž‰maęž‰ ba edaęž‰ha baęž‰bo kogaęž‰lamaęž‰naęž‰ ebe ibino Namutudawahaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰moe gabodo ibi haęž‰kiya ibi kokubahilamemaęž‰naęž‰, iyo, ibaęž‰te iyaęž‰tawahaęž‰ tetelo olalatiti ibi dito kopuwatemaęž‰ne.
\v 2 Huiyatiya olalatiti ibaęž‰tamo peheno, dopamo komo sose tawakalubi hiliyonomate kateneno ubi gabodo ibi ba taęž‰matale Godokono hibi gabo komiyaęž‰pamaęž‰naęž‰, iyo, baęž‰ba tetelo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te ibino kuba ododili komokomo ba ulamelelame Godokono hibi gabo kuba gabomaęž‰ baęž‰bo kogaęž‰lamaęž‰naęž‰.
\v 3 Baęž‰gala eta komo. Baęž‰bi haęž‰da tabo olamagimipaęž‰te ubi konomamo ihatena laęž‰eno mani haęž‰da gabodo uwatemaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibi haęž‰kiya ibino ukui komamo komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ uwi laęž‰ baęž‰bo kokiyahalamemaęž‰naęž‰ta. Huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, dopamo tetelo Godote ibino kuba huiya ikalamemaęž‰ hibilo aęž‰goiyaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰be kuba huiyate baęž‰ naęž‰pe, iyo, ibi Anakapulamedawate yaęž‰lo aęž‰hiduyaęž‰, ebete hido tete belatimina.
\s1 Godote Kuba Ododilipaęž‰tamo Huiya Ikalame Komo
\p 
\v 4 Baęž‰ hibila, Hunu Haboeno komo nopopaęž‰te Godokono tutumu dadikanaliyaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete ibi Saitanakono konomo du bobamo dito iyaęž‰hekiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te du ipuwalo auli halaęž‰mo matuhulameholaęž‰go ba emedehona ibino kuba huiya uwate hegela kolatiminamaęž‰.
\p 
\v 5 Baęž‰gala Nowate hopo habanapaęž‰tamo Godokono tuputupu emede komo dolamagiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te Godokono ubi komamo kapapamilaęž‰huyaęž‰haęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ Godote ibaęž‰tamo kuba huiya atumu ka-ikalamiyaęž‰, iyo, ebete hulama beya baęž‰moe hopamo daęž‰poemiyaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ibi hiliyonomate aęž‰haęž‰lahuyaęž‰, huiyatiya Nowate komo saęž‰baęž‰ni tawakalubaęž‰go ibi kapiyate kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo baęž‰bo lawiyaęž‰.
\p 
\v 6 Baęž‰gala Sodomo Gomola koko habalo demedehonamaęž‰, Godote baęž‰bi tawakalubaęž‰tamo kuba huiya ba ikalame koe powagoeno daęž‰poemiyaęž‰, ibi hiliyonomo koete baęž‰ dito pehawaminadigaliyaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, ibino olalati komo baęž‰ gola, Godokono ubi komamo papamilaęž‰halehaęž‰paęž‰tamo kuba huiyate keba kaęž‰na duluhukumini.
\v 7-8 Baęž‰ba tetelo Godote Sodomo habanapino kuba ododili mabumaęž‰ ibi hiliyonomo ba anakapulame tuputupu dubu Lotokono kaęž‰kaęž‰ kapiya bemulaęž‰miyaęž‰, mabu baęž‰be dubuti ibi ipuwalo ba emedena ibino kateneno kuba ubi komokomomaęž‰ tepo menemene daęž‰lawenakui ibino kuba ododili ipuwamo kopeganakuihaęž‰. Iyo, ebete ibaęž‰godolo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba ododili komo dulamenakui baęž‰gala ibino kuba tabo gaęž‰la komo dulihonakui, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete ebeno tepo ipuwalo ko temetemenomo biyaęž‰tawanakui. \fig Sodomo habanapino olalati komo baęž‰ gola|alt="Six people rushing from burning city" src="CO00656B.TIF" size="col" loc="3/4 of page on right hand side in corner" copy="1978 David C. Cook Publishing Co." ref="2.6"\fig*
\p 
\v 9 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, Godoko iyaęž‰tawala puyaęž‰te ebeno ubi komamo daęž‰papamilaęž‰hana baęž‰bi tawakalubino temeteme ipuwalo ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ komulaęž‰lelamemaęž‰. Baęž‰gala ebe iyaęž‰tawala ebete kuba ododilipi ibino olalati komamo matuhulameholete ibi Kuititi Hegela tetaęž‰mo komagatalemaęž‰ne ibaęž‰te kuba huiya baęž‰bo konuwatemaęž‰.
\v 10 Iyo, puyaęž‰te ibino hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kateneno dalowaęž‰ ubi ipuwalo ba wapataęž‰lamena Godotamo papamilaęž‰hale ubihaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, Godote baęž‰bako tawakalubaęž‰tamo kuba huiya konomamo hibinomolo kikalamemaęž‰ne.
\s1 Godokono Mahilamo Haęž‰da Tabo Olamagimipino Kuba Emede Komo
\p Numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰bi kuba ododilipi baęž‰ Godokono mahilamo haęž‰da tabo olamagimipila. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibino emede komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰nala, ibi haęž‰kiya ibi hunamo wadiyaęž‰paaęž‰latelelo Hunu Haboeno nopopi katolelamenahaęž‰, iyo, ibaęž‰te ibi biduduputilamenaka.
\v 11 Huiyatiya Godokono nopopino komo hiyaęž‰la, ibaęž‰te ebe tolemelo ebeno holoholo hapulu baęž‰bako kuba ukuiaęž‰gopi iduduputilameheno ibi kubapimaęž‰ akagaęž‰lalaęž‰, mabu ibi iyaęž‰tawahala komopino komo anagilamelelame oko baęž‰ Godokono okola, ibino okohaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰bi nopopino helo konomote hopo tawakalubino helo naęž‰gogolona, huiyatiya ibaęž‰te baęž‰be komo ba iyaęž‰tawaha ibi haęž‰kiya ibi kawagaminalenahaęž‰.
\v 12 Aęž‰iye, baęž‰ma tetelo daęž‰mahilaęž‰halena baęž‰bi haęž‰da tabo olamagimipino komo eba kaęž‰nahaęž‰! Ibaęž‰te Godokono hibi komo iyaęž‰tawahaheno, ebeno hidohido komomaęž‰ kuba tabo baęž‰bemaęž‰ gaęž‰lanaka. Iyo, ibi baęž‰ tumu goegoe keba kaęž‰nalaęž‰kaęž‰ ukuihino baęž‰ba kaęž‰na emedehona, baęž‰bemaęž‰ pomolo dubate baęž‰bako goegoe gubi ipuwalo uwateholete keba kaęž‰na kanakapulamenaka, ibino kuititi tete baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na kuluhukumaęž‰ne.
\p 
\v 13 Mabu ibaęž‰te temeteme komopaęž‰tamo dito dikalamenaka, baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godote ibino kuba huiyamaęž‰ temeteme ibaęž‰tamo kikalamemaęž‰ne. Aęž‰iye! Ibaęž‰te naęž‰kalakalahana kateneno kuba ubi komokomo hegela tetelo hilopoheno kododilinamaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipino kapiyuimi poko baaęž‰ naha ipuwalo ibaęž‰te laęž‰go daęž‰polaęž‰namenaęž‰, ibi baęž‰ hido baaęž‰ ipuwalo daęž‰polaęž‰na baęž‰bi kuba nene huiyala, iyo, ibino ododili komamo laęž‰ haęž‰da kamiholamemaęž‰ ibaęž‰te konomo kalakala belawenaka.
\v 14 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, keba tetelo ibaęž‰te kamenakamena baęž‰gala bohelemele dulamenaka, kuba ododi ukui kapiyate ibaęž‰tamo baęž‰bo penako, iyo, ibaęž‰te kateneno kuba ododilimaęž‰ iyaęž‰wa kokonomola. Baęž‰bene puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo helohaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi gugudi Saitanakono kuba emogabuimi komamo magatalenaka, baęž‰gala ibi ipuwalo ibi haęž‰kiya ibi iyaęž‰tulamiyaęž‰ ibino tepo ipuwoeno ukuiti mani emalagidole komamo kopapamilaęž‰halenamaęž‰. Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ibi Saitanakono gugudila, iyo, Godote ibaęž‰tamo kuba huiya hibilo kikalamemaęž‰ne!
\p 
\v 15 Iyo, hibila, ibaęž‰te hido tuputupu gabo miyaęž‰pate, Biyokono gudu Baęž‰ilamako ebeno kuba ododili gabodo ebe baęž‰bana taęž‰matana. Baęž‰be dubuino komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰nala, ebete mani kokonomo uwatemaęž‰ ebeno ubi dihatiyaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete kuba ododi gabodo to baęž‰bo tupuimiyaęž‰.
\v 16 Huiyatiya Godote ebeno daedae ukui koduhimimaęž‰ ebeno donoki-goe ipuwane lumagino tabo madodamo ebe koamo kiyahamiyaęž‰, baęž‰be haęž‰da tabo olamagidawate Isalaela tawakalubaęž‰tamo eta kuba ododikapomaęž‰.
\s1 Godokono Mahilamo Haęž‰da Tabo Dolamagiminaka Ebete Ibaęž‰tamo Kuba Huiya Ikalame Komo
\p 
\v 17 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moi haęž‰da tabo olamagimipi dubu baęž‰ beya maęž‰pete gagalemaęž‰ dedaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala, mabu hopo tawakalubaęž‰te ibaęž‰godolo hido owalubi aęž‰kumaęž‰menaęž‰. Baęž‰gala hopote gagalemaęž‰ dedaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo konomo huhuti daęž‰watanako baęž‰bi bubuti dito kopokoaęž‰tahalemaęž‰naęž‰ huiyatiya wegolate aęž‰koamene, baęž‰bi dubu baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰nala mabu ibaęž‰te tawakalubaęž‰tamo giba aęž‰kikalamaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godote ibi mabumaęž‰ kebe du bobo konomo yaęž‰lo dododilamiyaęž‰, ebete ibi baęž‰bamo konoelamemaęž‰ne ibaęž‰te baęž‰bolo temetemaęž‰go konemedehonamaęž‰.
\v 18 Aęž‰iye! Ibaęž‰te hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ awagaha tabo komokomo baęž‰gala daedae ukui komokomo begaęž‰lanaka, baęž‰gala puyaęž‰te Godotamo ohobilaęž‰maęž‰ kuba ododili ipuwane kaęž‰maęž‰nomo daęž‰pikulaęž‰, ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi tawakalubi ibino kateneno ubi komamo gala kuwatete Saitanakono kuba gabamo baęž‰bo magatalenaka.
\v 19 Ibaęž‰te ibaęž‰tamo tutulu emede komo ikalamemaęž‰ ibi aęž‰kiyalamenaka, huiyatiya ibi Godokono hibi tutu ipuwalo kemedehonahaęž‰, mabu ibaęž‰te ibino kateneno ubi komoeno huiyahaęž‰ okopimaęž‰ edaęž‰hana. Iyo, hibila, lumagiti kebe kuba ododi komamo daęž‰papamiwatana, ebete baęž‰be komoeno okodawamaęž‰ edaęž‰na, ebegodolo tutulu emede komo puliyanomola.
\p 
\v 20 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ hidamo! Kebe tawakalubaęž‰te aeno Kodawa baęž‰gala Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono hibi komo ba iyaęž‰tawaha baęž‰moe hopoeno kuba ubi komone daęž‰pikuliyaęž‰, baęž‰bene kuba ubi komate ibi gala kamatuhulameholete, ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi kuba ododili komamo gala daęž‰kapapamilaęž‰halemenaęž‰, ibi niliya! Dopamo tetelo ibaęž‰te nanekelaęž‰mo kubadopomaęž‰ edaęž‰hanamaęž‰, huiyatiya galane ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ kuititi tetelo ibaęž‰te kubanomomaęž‰ kedaęž‰hamaęž‰naęž‰.
\v 21 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ numaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰bako tawakalubaęž‰te Godokono tuputupu gabo iyaęž‰tawahaęž‰maęž‰ nedaęž‰honatale, ibaęž‰te kuba huiya nanekelaęž‰mo buwatenaęž‰. Huiyatiya ibaęž‰te Godokono gabo ba iyaęž‰tawaha, ebete ibi ebeno talona ipuwalo kemedenamaęž‰ dikalamiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te baęž‰be tutumu gunimaęž‰mo dito ihilateliyaęž‰, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ibino olalati komote konomomaęž‰ kedaęž‰maęž‰ne!
\v 22 Baęž‰ hibila, Godokono mulu ukui tabote ibino komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na hawakalimina, â€śGahate kebe kuba ilina daęž‰dalohomene, ebete baęž‰be atu ilina gala dito kakanalemaęž‰ne,â€ť baęž‰gala eta mulu ukui tabote baęž‰ma kaęž‰na goena, â€śLumagiti ebeno dabi goe hidamo dukulamene, baęž‰be goete bulaęž‰i ipuwamo kanopegate baęž‰bo konilulugutihomaęž‰ne.â€ť
\c 3
\s1 Kodawa Yaęž‰suti Baęž‰moe Hopamo Hibilo Gala Kakapemaęž‰ne
\p 
\v 1 Naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe baęž‰ netewa tetemaęž‰ edaęž‰ nale laęž‰tamo leta oelame, iyo, baęž‰moi netewa leta ipuwalo laęž‰le Godokono tuputupu komokomo hidamo kemalagidolenamaęž‰, nale laęž‰ baęž‰bemaęž‰ iyaęž‰tulamemata.
\v 2 Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godokono ukui hawakalimipaęž‰te kebe komate ibino gala hapuni pikulihomaęž‰ dopamo dolamagiminakui, na ubila laęž‰le baęž‰bi talona okopino bukoeno tabo komokomo gala hidamo naęž‰kemalagidolaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰gala aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa, ebe baęž‰ aeno Kodawala, ebeno oelamepaęž‰te kebe tutumu tabo ebegodone uwatete laęž‰tamo dikalamiyaęž‰la, wadiyala laęž‰le baęž‰bi komomaęž‰ atumu ukui gala naęž‰kamiyaęž‰taęž‰laęž‰.
\p 
\v 3 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰moe ko komo hidamo niyaęž‰tawahalaęž‰. Baęž‰moe hopoeno kuititi tete ba tatali, komo hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰paęž‰te pikuliti ibino kateneno kuba ubi komamo baęž‰bo kopapamilaęž‰halemaęž‰naęž‰. Baęž‰bene ibaęž‰te laęž‰ walilatelelo
\v 4 baęž‰ma kaęž‰na kogaęž‰lamaęž‰naęž‰, â€śHibilaęž‰kaęž‰, Yaęž‰suti gala pemaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰goiyaęž‰? Ale ebe kuminahaęž‰, kebolo kemedena? Baęž‰moe hopo tupuimi mabuni pete baęž‰ma tetaęž‰mo puluhuku tawakalubaęž‰te dito emedehonamaęž‰, baęž‰gala eta hanohano komote aeno nabaęž‰tamo uluhukuhino ibaęž‰te baęž‰ dito haęž‰lahuyaęž‰!â€ť
\p 
\v 5 Aęž‰iye! Baęž‰bako tabo gaęž‰lapaęž‰te iyaęž‰tawahala yaęž‰lo tetenomolo Godote baęž‰moe hopo baęž‰gala alomo ebeno tabamo dododiliyaęž‰, huiyatiya ibaęž‰te ubihinola baęž‰be komo hibimaęž‰ midi. Numaęž‰laęž‰, Godote baęž‰moe hopo dododiyaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete gagale hopo kulukulu beya ipuwane uluhukutiti beyamo baęž‰bo ododiyaęž‰,
\v 6 baęž‰gala ebete eta tetelo hulama beya daęž‰poemiyaęž‰ baęž‰be atu beyamo pakala hopo haba konomo aęž‰kubahimiyaęž‰.
\v 7 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete kodakoda tabo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ihatiyaęž‰, baęž‰ma tetelo daęž‰polaęž‰na baęž‰moe hopo konomo baęž‰gala alomo ibaęž‰te ebeno ubi tetaęž‰mo modobolo kopolaęž‰namaęž‰, baęž‰bene puyaęž‰te ebetamo papamilaęž‰haęž‰pimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, ebete ebeno Kuititi Hegelalo baęž‰bi tawakalubino komo anagilamelelamete ibi ba hawaminadigale baęž‰moe hopo koaęž‰mo baęž‰bo kokubahimimaęž‰ne.
\p 
\v 8 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰moe kapiya ko komo akadodalaęž‰. Kodawa Godogodolo kapiya hegela baęž‰ kapiya taosene gogo huiyala, baęž‰gala kapiya taosene gogo baęž‰ kapiya hegela huiyala, baęž‰ma kaęž‰na gopowahi tete baęž‰gala gaęž‰gaęž‰nomo tete ebete kapiya tetenomomaęž‰ goena.
\v 9 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te daedae ukuilo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na daęž‰gaęž‰lana, â€śHopo kuititi aęž‰kuluhukamene,â€ť ibaęž‰te Kodawa Godokono komo hibilo kiyaęž‰tawahanahaęž‰. Iyo, Godote baęž‰moe hopoeno kuititi tetemaęž‰ hibilo daęž‰goiyaęž‰, baęž‰be komote ebeno ubi tetelo kopuluhukumaęž‰ne, huiyatiya numaęž‰laęž‰, ebete hopo habanapi malemalelo emalagidolelo tete baęž‰bemaęž‰ gaęž‰gimaęž‰tepana, mabu ebe ubila tawakalubi hiliyonomate ibino kuba ododili ipuwane ohobilaęž‰te kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo ebegodone kolawemaęž‰.
\p 
\v 10 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, Kodawa Godokono Ko Hegelalo Yaęž‰suti kopemaęž‰ne, pilo dubuti tawakalubino ulihohaęž‰ tetelo keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰penako baęž‰ba kaęž‰na. Baęž‰ba tetelo baęž‰moe hopo baęž‰gala hopoeno ilina hiliyonomate kapimilo dito kowibohomaęž‰naęž‰, baęž‰bene atu tetelo alomo baęž‰gala alomoeno koko ilinate konomo diyamago kowibohomaęž‰naęž‰, mabu helonomo koete baęž‰moi ilina hiliyonomo dito kohawaminadigalemaęž‰ne.
\v 11 Iyo, Godote baęž‰moi ilina hiliyonomo baęž‰moe gabodo kohawaminadigalemaęž‰ne, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala laęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te laęž‰eno emede ipuwalo talonapimaęž‰ edaęž‰halo ebe kapiyatamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakuyaęž‰laęž‰,
\v 12 baęž‰gala wadiyala laęž‰ laęž‰eno hidohido ododili komodo ebe nowalonalaęž‰ baęž‰be tetete tiyonomolo kopemaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, Godokono Ko Hegelalo helonomo koete alomo baęž‰gala alomoeno koko ilina kapimilo kupulaęž‰digalemaęž‰ne,
\v 13 huiyatiya kalakala konomola, baęž‰ba tetelo ebete a hibimaęž‰ midipi ebeno uli hopo haba baęž‰gala uli hunu haba a baęž‰bamo komagatoemaęž‰ne, baęž‰bolo ebeno tuputupu emede komo kapiyate kitanamaęž‰ne. Numaęž‰laęž‰, ebete dopamo baęž‰be hido komo ododimaęž‰ hibilo daęž‰goiyaęž‰, ale baęž‰be komoeno tete baęž‰bemaęž‰ latiminamaęž‰.
\p 
\v 14 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰ baęž‰be Ko Hegela ba latimina, wadiyala laęž‰eno ukui konomamo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na nihatenakuyaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰le Godokono holoholo hapulu ba laęž‰motaęž‰hana laęž‰eno hiliyonomo ododili komo ipuwalo eta kapiya dehaęž‰potonomo kubate aęž‰kitanamene. Iyo, laęž‰le ebeno tataba ipuwalo ba emedehona, modobohaęž‰ komopaęž‰te laęž‰eno eta kapiya ododi komo kubamaęž‰ gaęž‰la.
\v 15 Baęž‰gala aeno Kodawate tiyolo puluhukuhino, laęž‰ baęž‰moe komo nemalagidoluyaęž‰laęž‰ ebete tete naęž‰gaęž‰gimaęž‰tepana komo hopo habanapaęž‰te ibino kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo kolawemaęž‰.
\p Laęž‰ iyaęž‰tawahala Poloko baęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi ipuwalo aeno hido naniwi etala, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebete dopamo eta leta laęž‰tamo poemelo atu tabonomo beka-olamagi. Iyo, Godote kebe mulu ukui ebetamo dikamiyaęž‰ ebete baęž‰be mulu komamo laęž‰ yaęž‰lo owalubiliaęž‰ta,
\v 16 baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibila, nale kebe tabo dolamagimo, Polokono hiliyonomo leta ododili ipuwalo ebete aeno Kodawoeno pe komomaęž‰ baęž‰ atu tabo beka-olamaginako. Na iyaęž‰tawala, komo tetelo ebeno tabo komokomoeno ipuwa kodakoda hibinomola, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ komo daedae ukuiaęž‰gopi baęž‰gala hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo ukui gagagagamaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, baęž‰bakobako tawakalubaęž‰te ebeno taboeno ipuwa haęž‰da amihoho gabodo hawakalilamenaka. Numaęž‰laęž‰, ibaęž‰te atu gabodo Godokono Bukoeno komo tabo komokomomaęž‰ tawakalubi kubamo iyaęž‰tulamenaka, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ibi haęž‰kiya ibino ukui ba kubahilamena ibino olalati komote hibilo kopemaęž‰ne.
\s1 Pitate Leta Kuititi Hapulu Tabo Dolamagiyaęž‰
\p 
\v 17 Naeno hidohido mabulubaęž‰laęž‰, laęž‰le baęž‰bakobako tawakalubino haęž‰da amiho komo dopamo iyaęž‰tawahuyaęž‰mata, baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ hidamo! Puyaęž‰te Godokono tutumu tabo daęž‰wakalaminaka, na ubihinola ibaęž‰te ibino haęž‰da amiho komamo laęž‰ ba magatale, laęž‰le baęž‰ma tetelo kebe hibi gabodo olalatihino daęž‰tolamenama baęž‰be gabote laęž‰godone alatidi.
\v 18 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ laęž‰ aeno Kodawa baęž‰gala Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono komo ba iyaęž‰tawahana ebeno malemale ipuwalo napepehonalaęž‰. Wadiyala awagaha komote baęž‰ma tetelo baęž‰gala emedena emedena tetelo ebegodolo nitanamene!
\p Baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baęž‰baęž‰la. 
